Must Do questions level one.

1st:- Print 1 to n using recursion.

2nd:- Print n to 0 using recursion.

3rd:- Print even numbers in between 0 to n ;

4th:- Print odd numbers in between n to 0 in assending order;

5th:- Print factorials eg:- 3! => 3 , 3*2 = 6, 3*2*1  = 6;

6th:- Print sum of n natural numbers; 

7th:- Print Multiply n natual numbers;

8th:- Print Factorials of n numbers;

9th:- Fibonacci series;

10th:- Find the X^n (where stack heigth = n);

11th:- Find the X^n (where stack height = logn)